## GhanaNLP API

Base URL: `https://translation-api.ghananlp.org/v1`
Auth header: `Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: <GHANANLP_API_KEY>`

Translate: `POST /translate` `{ "in": "<text>", "lang": "en-tw" }` → string
TTS:       `POST /tts`       `{ "text": "<twi>", "lang": "tw" }` → audio binary

## Performance

Pre-cache all 10 Twi audio clips on page mount via `preloadTwiAudio()` in `src/lib/audio.ts`.
Play from cache on sign detection — zero latency.
